  "description" : "* Based on an adventure fantasy manga by http://anidb.net/cr81545 [Nara Ippei].\nHaving spent his childhood in the slums, http://anidb.net/ch148537 [Shinonome Hajime] desperately sought strength to survive. Now, he enjoys a peaceful and carefree life as a resident adventurer of the Komai Village. One day, during a quest, he ventured into a dungeon and finds a young girl being partially eaten by a weakest kind of monster, a slime! The girl`s name was http://anidb.net/ch148538 [Rirui]. Having been abandoned by her parents, she had no place to go and entered the dungeon alone in order to stay alive. Hajime couldn`t just leave her there, so he took her back to the village to live with him!\nSource: Crunchyroll\nNote: The first two episodes received an early screening at a special event on 12 December 2025 at Marunouchi Piccadilly in Tokyo. The regular TV broadcast started on 7 January 2026.",
